dct_title_s: Map of the west coast of Africa
dct_description_sm: compiled from official documents, by John Arrowsmith.

Map of the west coast of Africa, with relief shown by hachures./ Plate 53 from: The London atlas of universal geography, exhibiting the physical & political devisions of the various countries of the world, constructed from original materials. London : J. Arrowsmith, 1842-[1850].
